2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T06:29:59.000Z","msg":"開過fake news台,<br />\n將已證實係fake news D post掉晒入去<br />\n要fact check都可以入返去睇<br />\n並且唔會再係原先個台/吹水台/熱門到再出現<br />\n唔怕D人唔睇comment繼續推post炒車<br />\n有冇得諗"},{"pid":"69ed70fcab0acdd11f216b3197cb4dc690b136f0","tid":1577694,"uid":32485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T06:33:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e0fff09fe37752345cd916322765662386b8559","tid":1577694,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:01:37.000Z","msg":"【死全家系列】紅磡站跳軌一事可見有大量人惡意散發FAKE NEWS<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ecuaBS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ecuaBS</a>"}]}